{
  "stem": "27507.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there were those horrible contrasts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I think that the Germans were as well-- all too well-- all too well aware of that because that was later-- in 1942, in spring 1942, they were using the ghetto to turn films for anti-Semitic propaganda.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were bringing the cameras into the ghetto and film crews and were turning proper bits of film, which we didn't know exactly what it meant.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we didn't-- well, one didn't expect anything good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But one didn't know what it meant, but it was obvious that they were turning them in order to make films showing how the Jews are terribly selfish and how they don't-- are not solidarity with each other and how they are immoral and how they are horrible.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were turning all kinds of pictures where they were-- of the restaurants where there-- some people were eating, guzzling themselves and beggars dying of hunger next to it, precisely.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And pictures when they were herding men and women together and telling them to dance and maybe to undress and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm not su-- I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not 100% sure how we managed then to keep still relatively-- a relatively acceptable standard of living because, as I said, I'm not aware of being hungry.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- life was, of course, not exactly happy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- one has-- it was suffering deprivations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one couldn't go out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one was only too aware of everything that was happening, but we were not hungry ourselves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were not suffering a terrible deprivation ourselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think it was we were partly helped because-- well, obviously, because we still had got some money from before, and we still had some things and were-- [COUGH].",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
